<seg id="1049">The recursive method starts with 4 rays per pixel. if the difference between the color values exceeds the given threshold, then the pixel is divided into 4 sub-pixels, which are separately pursued and checked for further subdivision. the maximum depth of the recursion can be adjusted with the depth value.</seg>
